<bibRefCitation author="Lissovsky A" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" pagination="28 - 60" refId="ref9780" refString="Lissovsky A (2016) Lagomorphs and Rodents I. Family Ochotonidae. In Wilson DE, Mittermeier, RA (Eds) Handbook of the mammals of the world. Vol. 6. Lynx Edicions, Barcelona, 28 - 60." type="book chapter" year="2016">Lissovsky 2016</bibRefCitation>
