<bibRefCitation author="Schai-Braun S &amp; Hacklander K" box="[1014,1388,1210,1234]" pageId="10" pageNumber="297" pagination="62 - 148" refId="ref10288" refString="Schai-Braun S, Hacklander K (2016) Lagomorphs and rodents I. Fam- ily Leporidae. In: Wilson DE, Mittermeier RA (Eds) Handbook of the mammals of the world. Vol. 6. Lynx Edicions, 62 - 148." type="book chapter" year="2016">Schai-Braun and Hackländer 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
